**Aim_ ag_ texture_ funkytown**
==================
Hello there,
This map is optimized especially for Deathmatch.You'll find alot of stairs and ladder on different floors.
Before you ask, the skybox is made by myself and I used the dev texture pack from a "quest" uploader. If you have any suggestions or question. Please leave it in a comment.

-Have fun !

Installation
==================
To install, unpack the .rar file to:

"Steam\steamapps\USERNAME\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps"

Comment & Rate
==================  
Please add a comment and rate on my map.
Also tell me if you see any bugs. I'll try to fix them.
